titles.title: Dewey Mitchell: Session at La Conner, WA, recorded by Vi Hilbert and Thom Hess

descriptions.description: Contents: Dewey Mitchell (8/21/71): Session at La Conner, WA, recorded by Vi Hilbert and Thom Hess. Program has been divided into 8 tracks: Tr. 1 – (8:17) (Beginning Tape Side A) Tr. 2 – (8:25) Tr. 3 – (9:45) Tr. 4 – (5:57) Tr. 5 – (8:17) (Beginning Tape Side B) Tr. 6 – (7:17) Tr. 7 – (7:03) Tr. 8 – (9:48) From the Thom Hess Collection, Ethnomusicology Archives (UWEA 95-19.29) Un iversity of Washington, Seattle
